decision_conditions:
Condition : 9 - Prior to the commencement of the use hereby approved on the site a noise report shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority detailing noise resulting from the operation of the facilities and proposed mitigation measures. This shall include: 
 - Enclosure of main waste recycling facility operations ? fully sealed structures to east, north, west and roof with kingspan cladding panels; 
 - Enclosure of waste output point (end of the line) ? fully sealed structure to 
east, north, west and roof with kingspan cladding panels; 
 - Enclosure of picking station ? and provision of contiguous solid boundary 
from ground level of base of picking station; 
 -  3.5m solid boundary wall surrounding application site to northern, western 
and part of eastern boundary;  
- Enclosed concrete mixer plant - enclosed concrete batching operations ? 
single sheet steel cladding and covered conveyors; 
 - Rubber tyres on all mobile plant/machinery.
